<section class="section s2-content">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="s2-content__header">
      <h2 class="s2-content__heading">Why Juvéderm Is The Gold Standard For Non-Surgical Facial Rejuvenation</h2>
      <p class="s2-content__body">Transform your appearance with the most trusted dermal filler, delivered by board-certified experts who prioritize natural-looking results and your safety above all else.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="s2-content__features">

      <div class="s2-content__feature">
        <h3 class="s2-content__feature-title">Immediate and Long-Lasting Results</h3>
        <p class="s2-content__feature-desc">You'll see instant volume restoration and wrinkle reduction right after your treatment, with results that continue improving over 2 weeks as the filler integrates naturally. Juvéderm can last 12-24 months depending on the formula used, giving you exceptional value compared to other treatments that require frequent touch-ups.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s2-content__feature">
        <h3 class="s2-content__feature-title">Natural-Looking Enhancement</h3>
        <p class="s2-content__feature-desc">Juvéderm's smooth gel consistency blends seamlessly with your natural tissues to create subtle, beautiful results that enhance your features without looking overdone. Our expert injectors have an artistic eye for facial proportions and will customize your treatment to complement your unique bone structure and aesthetic goals.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s2-content__feature">
        <h3 class="s2-content__feature-title">FDA-Approved Safety and Proven Track Record</h3>
        <p class="s2-content__feature-desc">Juvéderm has been safely used in millions of treatments worldwide with an excellent safety profile. The hyaluronic acid formula is naturally compatible with your skin and can be reversed if needed. Our board-certified practitioners follow strict injection protocols to minimize risks and ensure optimal results.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s2-content__feature">
        <h3 class="s2-content__feature-title">Versatile Treatment for Multiple Concerns</h3>
        <p class="s2-content__feature-desc">Whether you want fuller lips, lifted cheeks, smoothed nasolabial folds, or enhanced jawline definition, Juvéderm offers specialized formulas for each area. We can address multiple aging concerns in one appointment, giving you a comprehensive facial rejuvenation that looks completely natural and balanced.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s2-content__header {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s2-content__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s2-content__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s2-content__features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .s2-content__feature {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-sm);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-surface, #faf9f7);
  }

  .s2-content__feature-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s2-content__feature-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s2-content__features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
